<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Home - Spontaneous Miscellaneous</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Handmade makes, completed projects, and items needing new homes.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f7f4ef;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text: #333333;
            --heading: #111111;
            --accent: #ca9b52;
            --border: #e8e2d8;
            --hero-overlay: rgba(38, 27, 14, 0.36);
            --content-max: 1140px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg);
            font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .container {
            width: min(var(--content-max), 100% - 48px);
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .site-header {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .header-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 72px;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .brand {
            color: var(--heading);
            font-family: "Dancing Script", cursive;
            font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .main-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 26px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .main-nav a {
            color: #222;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 400px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            background:
                linear-gradient(var(--hero-overlay), var(--hero-overlay)),
                url("https://misssponto.me.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/IMG_20230331_221027_321-white-e1680891701768.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
            font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 56px);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        main {
            padding: 56px 0 72px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto 46px;
        }

        .intro h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            color: var(--heading);
            font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
            font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 44px);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .intro p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 44px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .project-image {
            aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
            width: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }

        .project-content {
            padding: 18px;
        }

        .project-content h4 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: var(--heading);
            font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .project-content p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .center-cta {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 26px;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .site-footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #f2eee8;
            padding: 22px 0;
        }

        .footer-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer-socials {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-socials a {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .whatsapp-float {
            position: fixed;
            right: 16px;
            bottom: 16px;
            z-index: 20;
            background: #25d366;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .project-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 740px) {
            .container {
                width: min(var(--content-max), 100% - 28px);
            }

            .header-row {
                min-height: 64px;
            }

            .brand {
                font-size: 34px;
            }

            .main-nav {
                gap: 14px;
            }

            .main-nav a {
                font-size: 12px;
                letter-spacing: 0.6px;
            }

            .hero {
                min-height: 300px;
            }

            .project-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .footer-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-row">
        <h1 class="brand">Spontaneous Miscellaneous</h1>
        <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/posts">Completed Projects</a>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello There!</h2>
        <p>I'm Karima</p>
    </div>
</section>

<main>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <h3>Needing new Homes</h3>
            <p>
                Here is my collection of makes and odds bits for sale. I am a crafter, not a social media marketer.
                If you would like further details about anything, feel free to get in touch directly.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="project-grid" aria-label="Project highlights">
            <article class="project-card">
                <img class="project-image" src="https://misssponto.me.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/IMG_20230326_122236_086.jpg" alt="Completed project showcase">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h4>Completed Projects</h4>
                    <p>Work that has already found a home.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="project-card">
                <img class="project-image" src="https://misssponto.me.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/IMG_20220930_203429_061.jpg" alt="Current work in progress">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h4>Working One thing at a Time (ha!)</h4>
                    <p>Most of my work that I have kept, sold, or gifted.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </section>

        <div class="center-cta">
            <a class="btn" href="/posts">See all projects!</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-row">
        <div class="footer-socials">
            <a href="#">Facebook</a>
            <a href="#">X</a>
            <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            <a href="#">Pinterest</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<a class="whatsapp-float" href="https://wa.me/447429900530" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp me</a>
</body>
</html>
